title: Shirley Scott & Stanley Turrentine - Blue Flames (1964) Pres
description:
SHIRLEY SCOTT and STANLEY TURRENTINE - BLUE FLAMES

1. The Funky Fox (Shirley Scott)
2. Hips Knees 'An Legs (Scott)
3. Five Spot After Dark (Benny Golson)
4. Grand Street (Sonny Rollins)
5. Flamingo (Anderson-Grouya)

Shirley Scott - organ
Stanley Turrentine - tenor sax
Bob Cranshaw - bass
Otis Finch - drums

Recorded in Englewood Cliffs, NJ; March 31, 1964

1995 Prestige/Fantasy
